author: @lamaa_2394
text:
Let me tell you something... In my country there were multiple cases like this with artists. There was one person a male that was really famous and looked like a "lovely" person. 2 years ago there was a news article that spread that he r@ped multiple minor girls. 

Literally nobody expected that from him and by that you can see that you can't trust nobody. No matter how they act towards you. So many people are fake and after these types of things happening in my life and on social media, i now have a really hard time trusting people around me. Even to the point that i sometimes have trust issues towards my family.

Be careful people and only trust yourself. Don't give too much away of your private life or information. This life is mostly by surviving alone.

I know that there are still good people but i think there are 80% of bad people and 20% of good people. Just be careful and always be aware of your surroundings.
